Summary: Make date optional for tasks.
Keywords: 

	* planner.el (planner-create-task-from-info): Make date optional.
	(planner-create-task-from-buffer): Make date optional. Thanks to
	Alan Schussman and emacs-wiki-discuss for the suggestion. You can
	now specify a non-date as the date to make a task that is not
	associated with any date. Warning: Unscheduled tasks might be
	forgotten.

